
This test concerns study death-fr

It uses the 10 first lines of deces-1994.txt downloaded from https://www.data.gouv.fr/datasets/fichier-des-personnes-decedees

The person database was generated by program g5 with:
php run-g5.php enrich deathfr init
php run-g5.php enrich deathfr raw2sqlite 1994

select bday,dday from person;
+------------+------------+
|    bday    |    dday    |
+------------+------------+
| 1906-09-11 | 1991-12-31 |
| 1903-03-20 | 1991-12-31 |
| 1905-10-03 | 1992-01-01 |
| 1908-02-08 | 1992-01-01 |
| 1942-03-02 | 1992-01-01 |
| 1902-04-19 | 1992-01-05 |
